e><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>Ir a compat.css:</strong></span><br /><br />Buscar:<br /><div class="codeheader">Código: <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="return smfSelectText(this);" class="codeoperation">[Seleccionar]</a></div><code class="bbc_code">table.boardsframe td.info<br />{<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;width: 60%;<br /></code><br />Reemplazar por:<br /><div class="codeheader">Código: <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="return smfSelectText(this);" class="codeoperation">[Seleccionar]</a></div><code class="bbc_code">table.boardsframe td.info<br />{<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;width: 56%;<br /></code><br />Y eso creo que vendría siendo todo&nbsp; <img src="/assets/smf/smileys/pacman.png" alt="*&#58;v*" title="Pacman" class="smiley" />
